+# WHY: the forensic found that 17-34% of ENTAILED verdicts across runs were pure
+# web-crawl chrome ("URL Source:", "Markdown Content:", "Title:", "Split View",
+# "Cite Cite", "Views"), bare DOIs, and numeric table rows — and a literal NTSB
+# "Page not found" 404 body was judged ENTAILED because boilerplate trivially
+# entails itself ("Page not found" ⊨ "Page not found"). A self-entailing chrome
+# line is a faithfulness HOLE, not a finding: it inflates the verified count with
+# a non-claim that never asserted anything.
